<%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Your Complete Business Solution Partner</h1>
            <p>From business setup to accounting, tax services, and real estate - All Zone Corporate Services provides comprehensive solutions for all your business needs.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary">Our Services</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Consultation</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>About Marco</h2>
            <p>Your trusted business services professional</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="/marco photo.jpg" alt="Marco - Business Services Professional">
            </div>
            <div class="about-text">
                <h3>Marco Lye</h3>
                <p class="title">Managing Director</p>
                <p>With more than 27 years of experience in Sales, Business Development, and Corporate Services, Marco brings a wealth of knowledge and leadership to the team. His career has taken him across the Middle East, where he has gained a deep understanding of the region's business environment and federal systems.</p>
                
                <p>Marco is known for his strategic mindset and hands-on approach. He has extensive expertise in business setup processes—ranging from licensing and visa facilitation to documentation and compliance. His strong global network allows him to deliver efficient, tailored solutions for clients looking to establish or expand their presence in the region.</p>
                
                <p>As Managing Director, Marco is driven by a commitment to excellence, operational efficiency, and client success. His leadership continues to play a key role in the company's growth and strong reputation in the market.</p>

                <div class="insight-section">
                    <h4>My Insight</h4>
                    <p>At AZ Corporate Services, we are passionate about turning ideas into thriving enterprises and transforming spaces into opportunities. Founded with a vision to simplify the journey of entrepreneurship and property investment, we specialize in Business Setup and Real Estate Solutions tailored to meet the dynamic needs of today's market.</p>
                    
                    <p>Whether you're a budding entrepreneur looking to establish your first venture or an investor seeking the perfect property, our team brings deep industry expertise, local insights, and a commitment to excellence. From navigating legal frameworks and compliance to identifying prime locations and negotiating deals, we handle the complexities so you can focus on growth.</p>
                    
                    <p>We believe in building lasting relationships through transparency, integrity, and personalized service. Our approach is consultative, collaborative, and always client-first — because your success is our business.</p>
                    
                    <p>Let us help you lay the foundation for your future.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h4>300+</h4>
                        <p>Companies Served</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h4>$25M+</h4>
                        <p>Business Value Created</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h4>99%</h4>
                        <p>Client Satisfaction</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="certifications">
                    <h4>Certifications & Expertise:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-award"></i> Certified Public Accountant (CPA)</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i> Business Formation Specialist</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-medal"></i> Licensed Real Estate Professional</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Tax Strategy Expert</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Featured Properties Section -->
<section id="properties" class="properties">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>
            <p>Discover exceptional homes in prime locations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="properties-grid" id="featuredPropertiesGrid">
            <% if (featuredProperties && featuredProperties.length > 0) { %>
                <% featuredProperties.forEach(property => { %>
                <div class="property-card" onclick="window.location.href='/property/<%= property._id %>'">
                    <div class="property-image">
                        <img src="<%= property.images && property.images[0] ? property.images[0] : '/marco photo.jpg' %>" 
                             alt="<%= property.name %>">
                        <div class="property-status status-<%= property.status %>">
                            <%= property.status.replace('-', ' ').toUpperCase() %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="property-info">
                        <h3><%= property.name %></h3>
                        <p class="property-location">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                            <%= property.location %>
                        </p>
                        <div class="property-features">
                            <span><i class="fas fa-bed"></i> <%= property.bedrooms %> bed</span>
                            <span><i class="fas fa-bath"></i> <%= property.bathrooms %> bath</span>
                            <span><i class="fas fa-ruler-combined"></i> <%= property.sqft %> sq ft</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="property-price"><%= property.price %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="no-properties">
                    <p>No featured properties available at the moment.</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="properties-cta">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">View All Properties</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

